The paper discusses the detection of emerging research topics, which is a common theme in several sub-categories of computer science. However, the focus on analysing the dynamics of collaboration between research areas suggests that the paper is most likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.DL (Digital Libraries), which deals with the organisation, retrieval and analysis of large collections of digital documents. Other relevant sub-categories include cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.SD (Software Engineering) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
